Help of 'hyde post'

  Update post:
    hyde post update [file_name (regular expression also ok)]
    hyde post update all

  Remove post (file will be deleted, if this is not you want, please use draft):
    hyde post delete [file_name (regular expression also ok)]
    hyde post delete all

  View post informations:
    hyde post info [file_name (regular expression also ok)]
    hyde post info all